<ol>
<li><strong>Compare the post-occupancy (POE) results with expectation</strong></li>
<li>Compare <strong>actual performance with the required performance</strong> and explain good or bad performance</li>
<li>Determine if any fine-tuning is required to rectify bad performance</li>
<li>Compare <strong>actual operational costs with the estimated operational costs</strong> and explain good or bad performance</li>
<li>Compare <strong>actual water consumption with predicted consumption</strong> and explain good or bad performance</li>
<li>Compare <strong>actual waste reduction with predicted reduction</strong> and explain good or bad performance</li>
<li>Request the attendance of a senior representative of each of the main disciplines within the design and construction team at a workshop with the ownerâ€™s representative and the representative(s) of end-users</li>
<li>
<strong>Report to the Appointing Party on the first year of performance</strong> and the actions considered necessary to optimize the performance of the asset/facility</li>
</ol></div></div></div></div></div></div>